Enter element [0][1]: 2
Enter element [0][2]: 3
Enter element [1][0]: 4
Enter element [1][1]: 5
Enter element [1][2]: 6
Enter element [2][0]: 7
Enter element [2][1]: 8
Enter element [2][2]: 9

The 3x3 matrix is:
1	2	3	
4	5	6	
7	8	9	
